<h1>WELCOME TO RIDGE VIEW HOMES</h1>
<p>Ridge View Homes was founded in 2019 by Bettina Hussain, Director, with the main aim of inspiring future <p>residents of Ridge View Homes with our passion and whole hearted commitment to our care provision.</p>
<p> to help and support vulnerable adults to exceed their expectation in attaining their personal.</p> development and their short, mid and long term goals in life.

We offer not only premium care with high standards but to fully engage with our residents and their families. We aim to exceed your expectations in attaining their personal development alongside achieving all the comforts of a home</p>

